    <h2>Overnight Positioning Strategy</h2>
    <p>For traders and holders navigating the overnight session (Asia night / US morning crossover):</p>

    <h3>For $DKING Holders:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Don't panic.</strong> A -1% move in a day where BTC dropped -4.6% is a sign of strength, not weakness.</li>
        <li><strong>Monitor BTC.</strong> If Bitcoin holds $68K and recovers toward $70K, meme coins are likely to follow.</li>
        <li><strong>Watch volume.</strong> If $DKING volume stays above $50K, the organic interest is real.</li>
        <li><strong>Use the dip.</strong> If you've been waiting for a better entry, controlled DCA during pullbacks is a proven strategy.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>General Market:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Set stop-losses at BTC $66K ” if BTC breaks below, further downside is likely.</li>
        <li>Track Solana activity ” SOL holding above key support is a bullish signal for Solana-based meme coins.</li>
        <li>Prepare for potential US session reversal ” US morning trading often brings renewed volatility.</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="highlight-box">
        <strong>�œ˜ The King's Perspective:</strong> Evening pullbacks in the middle of a rally are normal ” healthy, even. The June 2 morning surge showed strong buying interest, and the evening correction revealed that $DKING has the strongest relative hands in the meme coin market. This is exactly the kind of price action that separates quality projects from pump-and-dump tokens. The summer rally isn't over ” it's just getting started.
